Italian.productsDescription:
Pimsleur Italian IV Comprehensive is an all new 30-unit course that replaces the order Italian Plus 10-unit course.

This Comprehensive program consists of thirty 30-minute lessons totaling 15 hours of spoken Italian language learning. It also includes one hour of Reading Lessons, designed to expand your vocabulary and to give you practice reading Italian.

This Level IV program builds upon skills taught in Pimsleur's Italian Levels I to III. You'll be speaking and understanding Italian with near-fluency and with a broad range of conversational skills. In this program, the pace of recall and conversation moves more rapidly, accelerating learning and further expanding your vocabulary.
